magnolia;1;A flower with four glistening grey petals. Sweet clear liquid pools in the blooming body. It is unknown how the magnolia blooms in such a dark environment, or how it retains so much liquid, but provides a moment of respite in the form of a drink.;A flower with four glistening grey petals. Sweet clear liquid pools in the blooming body. It is unknown how the magnolia blooms in such a dark environment, or how it retains so much liquid, but provides a moment of respite in the form of a drink. Precautions should be taken, nearby insects take liking to planting eggs in the liquid that provides their offspring with essential nutrients, as well as a host for passerby animals, should one come along and drink it.
